200
00:18:37,361 --> 00:18:38,578
Maggie.

201
00:18:40,615 --> 00:18:42,458
Itu berbeda.

202
00:18:42,533 --> 00:18:43,534
Tidak.

203
00:18:44,535 --> 00:18:45,878
